hat overall H over C ratios of\nSOM decrease with increasing aqueous alteration, and the estimate of H loss\nfrom the SOM is 10% to 30%. Organics seem to be a significant H2 source that\nmay have caused subsequent chemical reactions in the Tagish Lake meteorite\nparent body.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Nov 2021 01:42:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-22"}
