 and the pseudo gap phase are found to be nearly\nindependent of doping level and/or flat-band bandwidth. The relevance of these\nphases with experimental discoveries in the flat band quantum moir\\'e materials\nis discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Nov 2021 02:57:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Nov 2021 08:01:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 7 Jun 2022 05:52:12 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 30 Nov 2022 02:40:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-01"}
